{"tid":2168064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最想搵番嘅人生過客","createTime":"2020-08-21T13:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T17:18:48.000Z","uid":224730,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f2db0b267ae84af5d40c56816ee7327305ed4dc","tid":2168064,"uid":224730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"相信每個人回望番人生，都有好多昔日好友<br />\n但好多時候，可能因為一時意氣，或因誤會鬧交，<br />\n因為面子，大家就無再主動搵大家。<br />\n另外，可能又會掛住重色輕友，好少約朋友出黎<br />\n或者識到新圈子嘅人，而慢慢同舊朋友疏遠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你地有無一啲類似經歷，覺得好可惜，好後悔，都想分享下呢?<br />\n小編自己其實好想搵番一班中同聚舊，自己中六轉左學校就少搵佢地，慢慢無咁fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以留言或者tg搵我地呀，希望大家真係有機會係到都搵番你地嘅「過客」呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTG: esmileyhk"},{"pid":"23c7e4719d752df3d99baf289d6e1c9fe500cbdd","tid":2168064,"uid":77763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"小編？"},{"pid":"fbc4b3ae014e75a4bc0ab06430d9958a462a64fc","tid":2168064,"uid":33874,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"小編你老母呀？"},{"pid":"53ded6c3891be23b61d4d0d5d1b4959aeb446669","tid":2168064,"uid":224730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"23c7e4719d752df3d99baf289d6e1c9fe500cbdd","tid":2168064,"uid":77763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"小編？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"即係我自己的意思"},{"pid":"e20a666fb3c1b6ff18e624ef1ebc0a620428266c","tid":2168064,"uid":224730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fbc4b3ae014e75a4bc0ab06430d9958a462a64fc","tid":2168064,"uid":33874,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"小編你老母呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"一時打錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl